          h5.ui.header
            i.caret.right.blue.icon
            .content
              | Is this article an opinion piece?
              
          h5.ui.header
            i.caret.right.blue.icon
            .content
              | Does the article mention where the information they reported comes 
              | from?
            
          h5.ui.header
            i.caret.right.blue.icon
            .content
              | Are there other sources that are also reporting this news?
                      
          h5.ui.header
            i.arrow.circle.right.blue.icon
